g%20passive%20income%20isn't%20always%20as%20easy%20as%20it%20sounds%20%E2%80%94%20it%20takes%20time%20and%20money%20up%20front%2C%20and%20the%20benefits%20don't%20come%20overnight.%20But%20financial%20planners%20say%20it's%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20worthwhile%20pursuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20out%20how%20people%20are%20earning%20passive%20income%2C%20Business%20Insider%20asked%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-financial-advisors%5C%22%3Efinancial%20advisors%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20share%20their%20clients'%20top%20passive-income%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20House%20hacking%20and%20real%20estate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinancial%20planner%20and%20Facet%20Wealth%20cofounder%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffacetwealth.com%2Fabout%2Fbrent-weiss%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrent%20Weiss%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he's%20seen%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20his%20clients%20turn%20to%20real%20estate%2C%20more%20specifically%20house%20hacking%2C%20to%20generate%20passive%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20hacking%2C%20or%20buying%20a%20home%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20renting%20out%20a%20room%20or%20separate%20unit%20within%20the%20home%2C%20is%20a%20simple%20way%20to%20get%20into%20real%20estate%20investing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20passive%20income%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20No.%201%20thing%20we%20all%20talk%20about%20is%20real%20estate%2C%26quot%3B%20Weiss%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20I%20talk%20to%20my%20clients%20about%20real%20estate%2C%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20do%20it%2C%20they%20sometimes%20reconsider%20their%20overall%20goals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOftentimes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-invest-in-real-estate-make-money%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20real%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20require%20a%20higher%20down%20payment%20than%20buying%20your%20own%20home%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20extra%20work%20managing%20tenants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20hacking%20reduces%20those%20hassles%20while%20still%20generating%20income.%20%26quot%3BProbably%20half%20of%20my%20clients%20are%20now%20thinking%20about%20real%20estate%20differently%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20a%20sudden%20they're%20paying%20half%20their%20mortgage%20and%20creating%20additional%20income%20for%20their%20family.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Dividend%20investing%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20some%20shares%20of%20stocks%2C%20companies%20offer%20investors%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20profit%2C%20with%20each%20share%20earning%20an%20amount%20in%20cash%20periodically.%20While%20it%20likely%20won't%20be%20monthly%20income%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-dividends-are-taxed%5C%22%3Edividends%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20truly%20passive%20income.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDividend%20income%20is%20definitely%20one%20major%20source%20of%20passive%20income%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20clients%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Akeiva%20Ellis%2C%20a%20financial%20planner%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebemusedtv.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Bemused%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She's%20seen%20this%20from%20her%20high%20net-worth%20clients%2C%20but%20she%20said%20it's%20also%20growing%20in%20popularity%20with%20her%20younger%20clients%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20there's%20the%20appreciation%20and%20the%20capital%20gains%20that%20everybody%20is%20familiar%20with.%20But%20selecting%20companies%20that%20also%20give%20dividends%20to%20their%20shareholders%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20is%20another%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20investment%20portfolio%20where%20you're%20able%20to%20get%20income%20out%20of%20it%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EWe