%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hedda%20Muskat%20Ellen%20DeGeneres%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f2ae008988ee337ec42e863%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20producer%20Hedda%20Muskat%20spoke%20about%20working%20on%20DeGeneres'%20talk%20show.%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Blanchard%2FPatrick%20McMullan%20via%20Getty%20Images%2FChris%20Pizzello%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EIn%20early%20August%2C%20several%20other%20ex-employees%20of%20DeGeneres%20came%20forward%20to%20share%20their%20experiences%20with%20her%20on-set%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20producer%20Hedda%20Muskat%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewrap.com%2Fellen-degeneres-former-producer-culture-of-fear-host-aware-of-abuses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wrap%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fellen-degeneres-ex-producer-calls-her-toxic-host-fear-culture-2020-8%5C%22%3Eincident%20during%20a%20staff%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20new-at-the-time%20executive%20producers%20Ed%20Glavin%20and%20Mary%20Connelly%20were%20introduced%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20existing%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuskat%20said%20Glavin%20screamed%20at%20one%20member%20of%20staff%20in%20front%20of%20everybody%20else.%20%26quot%3BHe%20just%20went%20off%20on%20them.%20His%20whole%20face%20turned%20red%E2%80%A6We%20were%20stunned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20waiting%20for%20Ellen%20to%20say%20something.%20'Whoa%2C%20Ed%2C%20don't%20talk%20like%20that%2C'%26quot%3B%20Muskat%20said.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20know%20what%20she%20did%3F%20She%20giggled.%20She%20crossed%20her%20legs%20up%20on%20the%20chair%20and%20she%20said%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20guess%20every%20production%20needs%20their%20dog.'%20And%20from%20then%20we%20knew.%20Ed%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20barking%20dog%20%E2%80%94%20her%20dog.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20never%20seen%20this%20before.%20I%20had%20never%20been%20around%20a%20toxic%20host%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20former%20DJ%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Ellen%20Show%26quot%3B%20Tony%20Okungbowa%20shared%20a%20statement%20about%20his%20experience%20shortly%20thereafter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20the%20opportunity%20it%20afforded%20me%2C%20I%20did%20experience%20and%20feel%20the%20toxicity%20of%20the%20environment%20and%20I%20stand%20with%20my%20former%20colleagues%20in%20their%20quest%20to%20create%20a%20healthier%20and%20more%20inclusive%20workplace%20as%20the%20show%20moves%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Okungbowa%20wrote%20on%20Instagram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22instagram%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22instagram%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDeYxlXJwnN%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHey%20Guys%2C%20I%20hope%20you%20are%20all%20keeping%20safe%20out%20there%20during%20these%20trying%20times.%20I%20have%20been%20getting%20calls%20asking%20me%20about%20the%20Ellen%20Degeneres%20Show%20and%20I%20would%20like%20to%20address%20the%20time%20I%20spent%20there.%20I%20was%20on%20air%20talent%20from%202003-2006%20and%20from%202007%20-2013.%20While%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20the%20opportunity%20it%20afforded%20me%2C%20I%20did%20experience%20and%20feel%20the%20toxicity%20of%20the%20environment%20and%20I%20stand%20with%20my%20former%20colleagues%20in%20their%20quest%20to%20create%20a%20healthier%20and%20more%20inclusive%20workplace%20as%20the%20show%20moves%20forward.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Tony%20okungbowa%20(%40tokungbowa)%20on%20Aug%204%2C%202020%20at%209%3A53am%20PDT%3Ctime%20datetime%3D%5C%222020-08-04T16%3A53%3A21%2B00%3A00%5C%22%3EAug%204%2C%202020%20at%209%3A53am%20PDT%3C%2Ftime%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'The%20Ellen%20Show'%20had%20its%20season%2018%20premiere%20in%20September%202020%2C%20and%20DeGeneres%20addressed%20the%20allegations%20in%20her%20opening%20monologue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ellen%20DeGeneres%20Show%26quot%3B%20returned%20on%20September%2021%20after%20a%20summer%20hiatus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20learned%20that%20things%20happened%20here%20that%20never%20should%20have%20happened.%20I%20take%20that%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20DeGeneres%20began.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20say%20I%20am%20so%20sorry%20to%20the%20people%20who%20were%20affected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20I'm%20in%20a%20position%20of%20privilege%20and%20power.%20And%20I%20realized%20that%20with%20that%20comes%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20take%20responsibility%20for%20what%20happens%20at%20my%20show.%20This%20is%20'The%20Ellen%20DeGeneres%20Show.'%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20conversations%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20about%20the%20show%2C%20our%20workplace%2C%20and%20what%20we%20want%20for%20the%20future.%20We%20have%20made%20the%20necessary%20changes%20and%20today%2C%20we%20are%20starting%20a%20new%20chapter%2C%26quot%3B%20DeGeneres%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeGeneres%20was%20called%20out%20by%20people%20on%20social%20media%20in%20late%20October%202020%20for%20her%20'superhero'%20nurse%20costume%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeGeneres%20shared%20a%20clip%20of%20herself%20in%20the%20costume%20on%20X%2C%20along%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20costume%20this%20year%20is%20inspired%20by%20the%20real%20superheroes%20of%202020.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E