20of%20the%20bed.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20can%20schedule%20it%20to%20warm%20up%20before%20bedtime%2C%20cool%20down%20while%20you%20sleep%2C%20and%20warm%20up%20again%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20wake%20up.%20Your%20partner%20can%20set%20a%20different%20heating%20and%20cooling%20schedule%20for%20their%20side.%20The%20heating%20system%20made%20a%20noticeable%20noise%20when%20engaged.%20My%20wife%20joked%20that%20it%20was%20like%20jet%20engines%20starting%20up.%20Yet%2C%20at%20no%20time%20did%20the%20bed's%20noises%20disrupt%20our%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20is%20also%20useful%20for%20adjusting%20the%20incline%20of%20the%20bed%20frame%20that%20the%20Climate360%20comes%20with.%20You%20can%20also%20select%20your%20%26quot%3BSleep%20Number%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%2020%20firmness%20options.%20My%20Sleep%20Number%20was%2055%2C%20a%20smidge%20firmer%20than%20average.%20This%20provided%20my%20ideal%20comfort%20and%20support%20while%20side%20sleeping.%20As%20I%20shifted%20positions%2C%20the%20air%20automatically%20adjusted%20to%20keep%20the%20support%20consistent%2C%20nurturing%20outstanding%20sleep%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20track%20my%20sleep%20quality%20using%20a%20smartwatch%2C%20but%20the%20Climate360%20has%20a%20built-in%20sleep%20tracker%20that%20produces%20accurate%20metrics.%20The%20app%20offers%20sleep%20advice%20based%20on%20your%20stats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20the%20Sleep%20Number%20Climate360%20Smart%20Bed%20in%20split%20king%20size%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20two%20twin%20XL%20mattresses%20next%20to%20each%20other.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20the%20bed%20had%20the%20best%20motion%20isolation%20I've%20ever%20tested.%20It%20easily%20passed%20the%20bowling%20ball%20test%20and%20had%20the%20lowest%20vibrometer%20reading.%20I%20was%20well%20supported%20when%20lying%20on%20the%20edge%2C%20but%20the%20side%20sank%20more%20than%20average%20when%20I%20sat%20on%20it.%20Still%2C%20this%20is%20the%20best%20luxury%20mattress%20for%20couples%20who%20can%20afford%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20mattresses%20for%20couples%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20whole%20guide%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-choose-a-mattress%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20choose%20a%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20differences%20between%20mattress%20types%20and%20firmness%20recommendations%20based%20on%20sleeping%20styles%20and%20body%20type.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20section%2C%20I%20focus%20on%20specific%20characteristics%20couples%20should%20consider%20based%20on%20my%20five%20years%20of%20testing%20mattresses%20and%20my%20interviews%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Floganschneider%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELogan%20Schneider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20clinical%20associate%20professor%20of%20sleep%20medicine%20at%20Stanford%20Sleep%20Center%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rebecca-robbins.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERebecca%20Robbins%2C%20PhD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20associate%20scientist%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brighamandwomens.org%2Fmedicine%2Fsleep-and-circadian-disorders%2Foverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrigham%20and%20Women's%20Hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20instructor%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhms.harvard.edu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Medical%20School%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESchneider%20recommends%20choosing%20a%20mattress%20large%20enough%20for%20both%20people%20to%20sleep%20undisturbed.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20always%20get%20closer%20on%20a%20larger%20mattress%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20get%20further%20away%20on%20a%20small%20mattress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20For%20an%20average-sized%20adult%2C%20that's%20a%20queen%20or%20larger.%20Check%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fmattress-size-chart%5C%22%3Emattress%20size%20chart%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20detailed%20recommendations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEdge%20support%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGood%20edge%20support%20goes%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20size%20because%20it%20gives%20you%20more%20space%20to%20sleep%20comfortably.%20You%20don't%20want%20to%20feel%20like%20you'll%20fall%20off%20the%20bed%20when%20your%20partner%20encroaches%20on%20your%20side.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotion%20isolation%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BMovement%20itself%20can%20be%20disruptive%20to%20the%20other%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schneider.%20He%20recommends%20finding%20a%20mattress%20that%20dampens%20motion%20transfer%20so%20that%20your%20sleep%20isn't%20disturbed%20when%20your%20partner%20tosses%20and%20turns%20in%20the%20night.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20comfortable%20bed%20is%20crucial%20for%20a%20good%20night's%20sleep.%20If%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20have%20similar%20firmness%20preferences%2C%20this%20isn't%20a%20problem.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20have%20drastically%20different%20needs%2C%20consider%20an%20adjustable%20airbed%20with%20different%20firmness%20levels%20on%20each%20side.%20If%20this%20isn't%20an%20option%2C%20choose%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20long%2C%20risk-free%20home%20trial%20so%20you%20can%20return%20it%20if%20it%20doesn't%20fit%20your%20needs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20movement%20and%20bounce%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20features%20are%20helpful%20for%20sexually%20active%20couples.%20They%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20change%20positions%20and%20engage%20in%20intimate%20activities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESchneider%20and%20Robbins%20said%20couples%20should%20consider%20sleeping%20apart%20to%20improve%20their%20sleep%20quality.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20means%20sleeping%20in%20different%20bedrooms%2C%20either%20because%20one%20partner%20snores%20or%20one%20partner%20isn't%20happy%20with%20the%20mattress%2C%20then%20that%20is%20absolutely%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robbins.%20%26quot%3BFurthermore%2C%20it%20will%20allow%20you%20to%20be%20a%20better%20partner%20to%20the%20person%20that%20you%20share%20your%20life%20with.%20So%20really%2C%20prioritizing%20sleep%20is%20really%20critical%20for%20couples.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20went%20through%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fsleep-divorce-sleeping-separately-advice%5C%22%3Esleep%20divorce%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20are%20much%20happier%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20mattresses%20for%20couples%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221622%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20sits%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20measures%20how%20much%20it%20sinks%20using%20a%20yardstick.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f1f78257bff70019486b34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221216%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20use%20a%20yardstick%20to%20measure%20how%20much%20the%20bed's%20edge%20sinks%20when%20I%20sit%20on%20it.%20I%20also%20measure%20edge%20support%20by%20seeing%20how%20close%20to%20the%20edge%20I%20can%20roll%20before%20falling%20off.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20slept%20on%20all%20mattresses%20in%20this%20guide%20for%2014%20nights%20or%20more.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20put%20them%20through%20several%20objective%20tests%20to%20assess%20their%20suitability%20for%20couples%2C%20including%20tests%20for%20comfort%2C%20motion%20dampening%2C%20and%20edge%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20test%20results%20for%20the%20main%20attributes%20we%20tested%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E