E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDjokovic%2C%2037%2C%20can%20equal%20Roger%20Federer's%20record%20of%20eight%20Wimbledon%20titles%20and%20become%20the%20tournament's%20oldest%20champion%20of%20the%20modern%20era%20if%20he%20avenges%20last%20year's%20dramatic%20five-set%20final%20loss%20to%20Alcaraz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Djokovic%20and%20Musetti%20met%20was%20at%20the%20French%20Open%20in%20June%20when%20the%20Serb%20claimed%20victory%20in%20a%20third%20round%20tie%20which%20ended%20at%203%3A07%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20however%2C%20Djokovic%20was%20untroubled%20on%20his%20way%20to%20a%2037th%20Grand%20Slam%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20broke%20for%204-2%20lead%20in%20the%20opener%20and%2C%20despite%20surrendering%20the%20advantage%20and%20letting%20two%20set%20points%20slip%20in%20the%20ninth%20game%2C%20he%20broke%20again%20in%20the%2010th%20to%20claim%20the%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20seed%20was%20playing%20in%20his%2049th%20Grand%20Slam%20semi-final%20while%20the%2022-year-old%20Musetti%20was%20in%20his%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20experience%20was%20key%20as%20Djokovic%20hit%20back%20from%20losing%20serve%20in%20the%20opening%20game%20of%20the%20second%20set%20to%20level%20in%20the%20sixth%20before%20dominating%20the%20tie-break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20break%20in%20the%20opening%20game%20of%20the%20third%20set%20launched%20him%20on%20his%20way%20to%20victory%20against%20a%20demoralised%20Musetti%2C%20who%20at%20least%20had%20the%20consolation%20of%20saving%20three%20match%20points%20before%20Djokovic%20completed%20his%20progress%20to%20yet%20another%20Wimbledon%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20world%20number%20three%20Alcaraz%20beat%20his%20fifth-ranked%20opponent%206-7%20(1%2F7)%2C%206-3%2C%206-4%2C%206-4%20and%20will%20face%20either%20seven-time%20champion%20Novak%20Djokovic%20or%20Lorenzo%20Musetti%20for%20the%20title%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlcaraz%20defeated%20Djokovic%20in%20the%202023%20final%20in%20a%20five-set%20thriller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%20it%20will%20be%20a%20really%20difficult%20match.%20Let's%20see%20who%20I%20am%20going%20to%20play%20on%20Sunday%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alcaraz%20who%20crunched%2055%20winners%20to%20the%2031%20from%20Medvedev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I%20am%20not%20new%20anymore.%20I%20know%20how%20I%20am%20going%20to%20feel%20before%20the%20final.%20I%20have%20been%20in%20this%20position%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20really%20nervous%20today.%20Daniil%20was%20dominating%20the%20match%2C%20playing%20great%20tennis.%20It%20was%20difficult%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwice%20Medvedev%2C%20beaten%20by%20the%20Spaniard%20at%20the%20same%20stage%20last%20year%2C%20led%20with%20breaks%20in%20the%20first%20set%20only%20to%20be%20pinned%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20his%20frustration%20that%20he%20was%20handed%20a%20warning%20for%20unsportsmanlike%20conduct%20by%20umpire%20Eva%20Asderaki%20for%20an%20apparent%20foul-mouthed%20reaction%20to%20a%20ball%20called%20for%20bouncing%20twice%20as%20he%20was%20broken%20in%20the%20ninth%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tournament%20referee%20and%20supervisor%20were%20even%20summoned%20to%20Centre%20Court%20by%20Asderaki%2C%20but%20Medvedev%20shrugged%20off%20the%20incident%20to%20sweep%20through%20the%20tie-break%20and%20take%20the%20opening%20set%20in%20which%20he%20committed%20only%20eight%20unforced%20errors%20to%20the%20Spaniard's%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20third%20time%20at%20this%20year's%20Wimbledon%20that%20Alcaraz%20had%20dropped%20the%20first%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlcaraz%20recovered%20impressively%2C%20breaking%20Medvedev%20for%20a%203-1%20lead%20in%20the%20second%2C%20having%20come%20out%20on%20top%20in%20the%20previous%20game%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%2027-shot%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2021-year-old%20then%20hit%2014%20winners%20in%20the%20third%20set%2C%20pocketing%20the%20only%20break%20in%20the%20third%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedvedev%2C%20who%20had%20knocked%20out%20world%20number%20one%20Jannik%20Sinner%20in%20the%20quarter-finals%2C%20retrieved%20a%20break%20early%20in%20the%20fourth%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Alcaraz%20kept%20up%20his%20assault%2C%20edging%20ahead%20again%20for%204-3%20on%20his%20way%20to%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20AFP%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720811220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fvqsal39o_novak-djokovic-wimbledon_625x300_12_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2024%2Fnovak-djokovic-marches-past-lorenzo-musetti-sets-up-wimbledon-mens-singles-final-clash-with-carlos-alcaraz-6093652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Novak%20Djokovic%20beats%20Lorenzo%20Musetti%206-4%2C%207-6%2C%206-4%20in%20men's%20singles%20semifinal%2C%20to%20face%20Carlos%20Alcaraz%20in%20Wimbledon%202024%20final.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2024%2Fnovak-djokovic-marches-past-lorenzo-musetti-sets-up-wimbledon-mens-singles-final-clash-with-carlos-alcaraz-6093652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2024%2Fnovak-djokovic-marches-past-lorenzo-musetti-sets-up-wimbledon-mens-singles-final-clash-with-carlos-alcaraz-6093652%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwimbledon-2024%2Fnovak-djokovic-marches-past-lorenzo-musetti-sets-up-wimbledon-mens-singles-final-clash-with-carlos-alcaraz-6093652%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Many%20Democrats%20are%20sticking%20with%20Biden.%20Here's%20why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720811093000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F9401%2Flive%2F4d46d420-4055-11