Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20abuse%20animals%20are%20often%20shown%20to%20have%20no%20regard%20for%20human%20life%2C%20either.%20For%20the%20sake%20of%20everyone's%20safety%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20members%20of%20the%20public%20report%20cases%20of%20cruelty%20to%20animals%20such%20as%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PETA%20India%20Cruelty%20Response%20Coordinator%20Sinchana%20Subramanyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720806420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fc2vqsr18_man-bites-off-hen-head-instagram_625x300_12_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdancer-bites-off-hen-head-during-performance-in-andhra-pradesh-fir-filed-6091715%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Police%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20a%20dancer%20for%20killing%20a%20hen%20by%20biting%20off%20its%20head%20during%20a%20performance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdancer-bites-off-hen-head-during-performance-in-andhra-pradesh-fir-filed-6091715%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdancer-bites-off-hen-head-during-performance-in-andhra-pradesh-fir-filed-6091715%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdancer-bites-off-hen-head-during-performance-in-andhra-pradesh-fir-filed-6091715%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Inc%20files%20ECB%20intent%20worth%20%244.28%20billion%20in%20May%2C%20shows%20RBI%20data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720805624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2016-12%2F26%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1482700963-9538.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-inc-files-ecb-intent-worth-4-28-billion-in-may-shows-rbi-data-124071201272_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Out%20of%20this%2C%20the%20intent%20for%20fund%20raise%20through%20the%20automatic%20route%20amounted%20to%20%24%203.66%20billion%20and%20that%20via%20approval%20route%20was%20%24%20343.2%20million%2C%20according%20to%20RBI%20data%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-inc-files-ecb-intent-worth-4-28-billion-in-may-shows-rbi-data-124071201272_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-inc-files-ecb-intent-worth-4-28-billion-in-may-shows-rbi-data-124071201272_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-inc-files-ecb-intent-worth-4-28-billion-in-may-shows-rbi-data-124071201272_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Enforcement%20Directorate%20Can't%20Arrest%20As%20Per%20Whims%20And%20Fancies%3A%20Top%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20power%20to%20arrest%20under%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20law%20cannot%20be%20exercised%20according%20to%20the%20whims%20and%20fancies%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20which%20granted%20interim%20bail%20to%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20excise%20policy%20scam%2C%20said%20any%20undue%20indulgence%20and%20latitude%20to%20the%20ED%20will%20be%20deleterious%20to%20the%20constitutional%20values%20of%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20life%20and%20liberty%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20officer%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20selectively%20pick%20and%20choose%20material%20implicating%20the%20person%20to%20be%20arrested.%20They%20have%20to%20equally%20apply%20their%20mind%20to%20other%20material%20which%20absolves%20and%20exculpates%20the%20arrestee.%20The%20power%20to%20arrest%20under%20Section%2019(1)%20of%20the%20PML%20Act%20cannot%20be%20exercised%20as%20per%20the%20whims%20and%20fancies%20of%20the%20officer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20its%2064-page%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20ED%20officers%20acting%20under%20Section%2019(1)%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20cannot%20ignore%20or%20not%20consider%20the%20material%20which%20exonerates%20the%20arrestee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20legality%20of%20the%20'reasons%20to%20believe'%20have%20to%20be%20examined%20based%20on%20what%20is%20mentioned%20and%20recorded%20therein%20and%20the%20material%20on%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20officer%20acting%20under%20Section%2019(1)%20of%20the%20PML%20Act%20cannot%20ignore%20or%20not%20consider%20the%20material%20which%20exonerates%20the%20arrestee.%20Any%20such%20non-consideration%20would%20lead%20to%20difficult%20and%20unacceptable%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20ED%20officer%20is%20undoubtedly%20subjective%2C%20but%20the%20formation%20of%20opinion%20should%20be%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubjectivity%20of%20the%20opinion%20is%20not%20a%20carte%20blanche%20to%20ignore%20relevant%20absolving%20material%20without%20an%20explanation.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20the%20officer%20commits%20an%20error%20in%20law%20which%20goes%20to%20the%20root%20of%20the%20decision-making%20process%2C%20and%20amounts%20to%20legal%20malice%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20made%20the%20observation%20as%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20ED%20has%20not%20mentioned%20in%20%26quot%3Bgrounds%20of%20arrest%26quot%3B%20the%20exculpatory%20statements%20made%20by%20the%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case%20and%20has%20only%20considered%20inculpatory%20statements%20in%20which%20he%20was%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20a%20view%20accepted%20in%20the%202022%20verdict%20of%20Vijay%20Madanlal%20Choudhary%2C%20which%20upheld%20the%20validity%20of%20PMLA%2C%20is%20that%20the%20order%20of%20arrest%20under%20Section%2019(1)%20of%20the%20PMLA%20is%20a%20decision%20taken%20by%20a%20high-ranking%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20high-ranking%20officer%20is%20conscious%20of%20the%20obligation%20imposed%20by%20Section%2019(1)%20of%20the%20PMLA%20before%20passing%20an%20order%20of%20arrest.%20We%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20it%20would%20be%20incongruous%20to%20argue%20that%20the%20high-ranking%20officer%20should%20not%20objectively%20consider%20all%20material%2C%20including%20exculpatory%20material%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20observed%20that%20a%20wrong%20application%20of%20law%20or%20arbitrary%20exercise%20of%20duty%20leads%20to%20illegality%20in%20the%20process%20and%20the%20court%20can%20exercise%20their%20judicial%20review%20to%20strike%20down%20such%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20not%20amount%20to%20judicial%20overreach%20or%20interference%20with%20the%20investigation%2C%20as%20has%20been%20argued%20by%20the%20DoE%20(Directorate%20of%20Enforcement).%20The%20court%20only%20ensures%20that%20the%20enforcement%20of%20the%20law%20is%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20statute%20and%20the%20Constitution.%20An%20adverse%20decision%20would%20only%20help%20in%20ensuring%20better%20compliance%20with%20the%20statute%20and%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20jurisdictional%20review%20permits%20review%20of%20errors%20of%20law%20when%20constitutional%20or%20statutory%20terms%2C%20essential%20for%20the%20exercise%20of%20power%2C%20are%20misapplied%20or%20misconstrued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudicial%20review%20is%20permissible%20to%20check%20improper%20exercise%20of%20power.%20For%20instance%2C%20it%20is%20an%20improper%20exercise%20of%20power%20when%20the%20power%20is%20not%20exercised%20genuinely%2C%20but%20rather%20to%20avoid%20embarrassment%20or%20for%20wreaking%20personal%20vengeance.%20Lastly%2C%20judicial%20review%20can%20be%20exercised%20when%20the%20authorities%20have%20not%20considered%20grounds%20which%20are%20relevant%20or%20have%20accounted%20for%20grounds%20which%20are%20not%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20that%20error%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process%20can%20vitiate%20a%20judgment%20or%20decision%20of%20a%20statutory%20authority%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20terms%20of%20section%2019(1)%20of%20the%20PMLA%2C%20a%20decision-making%20error%20can%20lead%20to%20the%20arrest%20and%20deprivation%20of%20liberty%20of%20the%20arrestee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20not%20akin%20to%20preventive%20detention%20cases%2C%20but%20given%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20order%20entailing%20arrest%20%E2%80%93%20it%20requires%20careful%20scrutiny%20and%20consideration.%20Yet%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20courts%20should%20not%20go%20into%20the%20correctness%20of%20the%20opinion%20formed%20or%20sufficiency%20of%20the%20material%20on%20which%20it%20is%20based%2C%20albeit%20if%20a%20vital%20ground%20or%20fact%20is%20not%20considered%20or%20the%20ground%20or%20reason%20is%20found%20to%20be%20non-existent%2C%20the%20order%20of%20detention%20may%20fail%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720804260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-cant-arrest-people-as-per-whims-and-fancies-supreme-court-6091964%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20power%20to%20arrest%20under%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20law%20cannot%20be%20exercised%20according%20to%20the%20whims%20and%20fancies%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-cant-arrest-people-as-per-whims-and-fancies-supreme-court-6091964%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-cant-arrest-people-as-per-whims-and-fancies-supreme-court-6091964%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-cant-arrest-people-as-per-whims-and-fancies-supreme-court-6091964%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Outgoing%20Nepal%20PM%20Approved%20China%20Rail%20Deal%20Ahead%20Of%20Trust%20Vote%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20Nepal%20Prime%20Minister%20Pushpa%20Kamal%20Dahal%20'Prachanda'%20lost%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence%20in%20Parliament%2C%20he%20gave%20a%20nod%20to%20an%20agreement%20to%20connect%20the%20Himalayan%20nation%20with%20China%20by%20rail%20under%20Beijing's%20ambitious%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20government%20sources%2C%20the%20MyRepublica%20news%20portal%20said%20this%20decision%20carries%20more%20operational%20than%20political%20significance%20and%20aligns%20with%20Nepal's%20participation%20in%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping's%20multi-billion-dollar%20pet%20infrastructure%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Cabinet%20meeting%20held%20on%20Thursday%20decided%20to%20approve%20the%20'Strengthening%20the%20Development%20Cooperation%20in%20Building%20the%20Trans-Himalayan%20Multidimensional%20Connectivity%20Network'%20agreement%20between%20Nepal%20and%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20quoted%20Communication%20Minister%20and%20the%20government's%20spokesperson%20Rekha%20Sharma%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20minister%20downplayed%20its%20immediate%20impact%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20initial%20decision%3B%20details%20of%20project%20implementation%20and%20BRI%20modalities%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20finalised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Prachanda'%20lost%20the%20vote%20of%20confidence%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Friday%20after%20coalition%20partner%20Communist%20Party%20of%20Nepal-Unified%20Marxist%20Leninist%20(CPN-UML)%20withdrew%20support%20for%20him%2C%20a%20development%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20government%20led%20by%20ex-prime%20minister%20K%20P%20Sharma%20Oli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrachanda%20received%20only%2063%20votes%20in%20the%20275-member%20House%20of%20Representatives%20(HoR)%20and%20there%20were%20194%20votes%20against%20the%20motion.%20At%20least%20138%20votes%20are%20needed%20to%20win%20the%20vote%20of%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20258%20HoR%20members%20participated%20in%20the%20voting%20while%20one%20abstained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrachanda's%20move%2C%20made%20just%20before%20he%20departed%20from%20office%2C%20is%20viewed%20not%20only%20as%20progress%20towards%20implementing%20BRI%20projects%20but%20also%20crucial%20for%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Kerung-Kathmandu%20railway%20and%20broader%20infrastructure%20development%20along%20the%20Nepal-China%20border%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20ahead%20of%20signing%20a%20power-sharing%20agreement%20with%20UML%2C%20the%20Nepali%20Congress%20had%20resolved%20to%20%26quot%3Bonly%20accept%20grants%20and%20not%20loans%20under%20the%20BRI%20project%26quot%3B.%20The%20government%20was%20also%20set%20to%20decide%20on%20implementing%20the%202017%20BRI%20agreement%20with%20China%2C%20which%20has%20been%20pending%20at%20the%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRI%20has%20raised%20global%20concerns%20over%20China's%20debt%20diplomacy%20of%20extending%20huge%20loans%20to%20smaller%20countries%20for%20unsustainable%20infrastructure%20projects.%20The%20Hambantota%20port%2C%20which%20was%20funded%20by%20a%20Chinese%20loan%2C%20was%20leased%20to%20Beijing%20in%20a%2099-year%20debt-for-equity%20swap%20in%202017%20after%20Sri%20Lanka%20failed%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20protested%20to%20China%20over%20BRI's%20%2460-billion%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20flagship%20project%20as%20it%20is%20being%20laid%20through%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720804140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fb9pqo8g8_nepal-pm-pushpa-kamal-dahal-prachanda-ani_625x300_06_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprachanda-belt-and-road-initiative-outgoing-nepal-pm-approved-china-rail-deal-ahead-of-trust-vote-report-6093132%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20before%20Nepal%20Prime%20Minister%20Pushpa%20Kamal%20Dahal%20'Prachanda'%20lost%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence%20in%20Parliament%2C%20he%20gave%20a%20nod%20to%20an%20agreement%20to%20connect%20the%20Himalayan%20nation%20with%20China%20by%20rail%20under%20Beijing's%20ambitious%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprachanda-belt-and-road-initiative-outgoing-nepal-pm-approved-china-rail-deal-ahead-of-trust-vote-report-6093132%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-