2Famericans-have-made-their-minds-ashley-judd-calls-on-biden-to-step-aside%2Famp_articleshow%2F111696236.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Famericans-have-made-their-minds-ashley-judd-calls-on-biden-to-step-aside%2Famp_articleshow%2F111696236.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20Congress%20MLAs%20Cross-Voted%20In%20Key%20Maharashtra%20Polls%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20worrying%20sign%20for%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20was%20riding%20high%20after%20winning%2030%20of%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20at%20least%20seven%20Congress%20MLAs%20cross-voted%20for%20candidates%20from%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20in%20the%20Legislative%20Council%20polls%20on%20Friday%2C%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%2C%20which%20are%20generally%20a%20straightforward%20affair%2C%20were%20seen%20as%20the%20semi-finals%20ahead%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%20-%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20around%20November%20-%20because%2012%20candidates%20were%20vying%20for%2011%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20alliance%20had%20forced%20the%20election%20by%20fielding%20one%20more%20candidate%20than%20it%20had%20the%20numbers%20to%20elect%2C%20possibly%20hoping%20to%20benefit%20from%20cross-voting%20by%20MLAs%20from%20the%20ruling%20coalition%2C%20but%20seems%20to%20have%20ended%20up%20losing%20votes%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20has%20a%20strength%20of%20288%20MLAs%20but%20currently%20has%20274%20sitting%20legislators.%20This%20meant%20that%20each%20MLC%20candidate%20needed%2023%20first-preference%20votes%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahayuti%20-%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20NDA%20alliance%20-%20which%20consists%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20wing%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20fielded%20nine%20candidates%20and%20had%20201%20MLAs%2C%20including%20Independents%20and%20smaller%20parties%2C%20backing%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20INDIA%20umbrella%2C%20has%20the%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20and%20the%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20as%20its%20key%20constituents%20and%20had%20put%20up%20three%20candidates%20despite%20having%20the%20support%20of%20only%2067%20MLAs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20MLAs%2C%20including%20an%20independent%2C%20were%20neutral.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20was%20hoping%20that%20it%20would%20get%20some%20votes%20from%20the%20Mahayuti%2C%20especially%20amid%20the%20buzz%20of%20some%20leaders%20from%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20NCP%20group%20being%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candidate%20backed%20by%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%2C%20Jayant%20Patil%20of%20the%20Peasants%20and%20Workers%20Party%2C%20however%2C%20lost%20because%20he%20did%20not%20get%20enough%20votes.%20The%20Congress%20candidate%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20candidate%20sailed%20through%2C%20as%20did%20five%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20two%20each%20from%20the%20Shinde%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%2037%20MLAs%2C%20had%20fixed%20a%20quota%20of%2030%20first-preference%20votes%20for%20its%20candidate%20Pradyna%20Satav%2C%20and%20seven%20remaining%20votes%20were%20to%20go%20to%20Milind%20Narvekar%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Satav%20got%2025%20first%20preference%20votes%20and%20Mr%20Narvekar%20got%2022%2C%20which%20means%20at%20least%20seven%20Congress%20MLAs%20cross-voted%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720802580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Feof4snsk_maharashtra-assembly-_625x300_27_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22h