ET%20Case%20Accused%20Claims%20%26quot%3BMistaken%20Identity%26quot%3B%20Led%20To%20CBI%20Arrest%2C%20Gets%20Bail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20on%20Friday%20granted%20bail%20to%20one%20Gangadhar%20Gunde%20whose%20counsel%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20wrongly%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20due%20to%20mistaken%20identity%20in%20an%20NEET%20paper%20case%20linked%20to%20Latur%2C%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBI%20had%20arrested%20the%20accused%20Gunde%20on%20June%2026%20from%20Dehradun.%20This%20case%20was%20initially%20registered%20by%20the%20Latur%20Police%20at%20Shivaji%20Nagar%20Police%20Station.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20FIR%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20CBI%20judge%20Ankit%20Singla%20granted%20bail%20to%20Gangadhar%20Gunde%20after%20hearing%20arguments%20of%20counsel%20for%20CBI%20and%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%20on%20furnishing%20of%20a%20bail%20bond%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20and%20a%20surety%20bond%20of%20the%20same%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Kailash%20More%20counsel%20for%20Gangadhar%20Rangnath%20Gunde%20argued%20that%20Gunde%20had%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20June%2026%20from%20Dehradun%20due%20to%20mistaken%20identity.%20He%20is%20not%20the%20actual%20man%20for%20whom%20CBI%20was%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20submitted%20that%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20by%20the%20CBI%20about%20the%20NEET%20UG%20exam%202024%20against%20a%20person%20whose%20name%20is%20also%20Gangadhar%20but%20the%20full%20name%20was%20not%20revealed.%20N%20Gangadhar%20Appa%20Nanjuthappa%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20later%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBI%20had%20lodged%20the%20case%20against%20unknown%20persons.%20N%20Gangadhar%20Appa%20Nanjuthappa%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20More%20also%20submitted%20that%20Gangadhar%20Gunde's%20name%20surfaced%20during%20the%20investigation%20as%