er%20and%20he%20is%20Delhi%20Delhi-based%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20man%20N%20Gangadhar%20Nanjuthappa%20also%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20accused%20namely%20Irenna%20Konagalwar%20is%20on%20the%20run%2C%20only%20he%20can%20identify%20who%20is%20real%20Gangadhar%2C%20the%20agency%20looking%20for%2C%20CBI%20counsel%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20submitted%20that%20Gangadhar's%20phone%20CDR%20is%20also%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20referring%20to%20the%20conspiracy%20aspects%20the%20CBI%20counsel%20submitted%20that%20Jadhav%20and%20Pathan%20were%20contacting%20and%20collecting%20initial%20token%20money%20and%20admit%20cards%20from%20the%20NEET%20Aspirants.%20They%20were%20sending%20the%20same%20to%20Irenna%20Konagalwar%20who%20in%20turn%20gave%20it%20to%20Gangadhar%20who%20lives%20in%20Delhi%20to%20get%20their%20marks%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20submitted%20that%20Gunde%20was%20arrested%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20June%2025%20and%2026%20in%20Dehradun%20in%20one%20of%20the%20five%20cases%20registered%20by%20the%20CBI.%20He%20was%20produced%20before%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20Court%20on%20June%2027%20and%20was%20remanded%20to%20CBI%20custody%20till%20June%2030.%20Thereafter%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20on%20July%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720797360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fatt9hsso_court-generic_625x300_27_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-case-accused-claims-mistaken-identity-led-to-cbi-arrest-gets-bail-6092458%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20on%20Friday%20granted%20bail%20to%20one%20Gangadhar%20Gunde%20whose%20counsel%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20wrongly