akhand's%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20is%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20data%20provided%20by%20live-in%20couples%20remains%20protected%20but%20feels%20that%20information%20about%20those%20aged%20between%2018%20and%2021%20should%20be%20given%20to%20their%20parents%2C%20the%20committee's%20chief%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UCC%2C%20passed%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Assembly%20in%20February%2C%20makes%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20and%20marriages%20mandatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20report%20of%20an%20expert%20committee%20constituted%20to%20draft%20UCC%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Justice%20(retd)%20Ranjana%20Prakash%20Desai%20was%20uploaded%20on%20the%20website%20www.ucc.uk.gov.in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-member%20panel%20headed%20by%20Ms%20Desai%20was%20constituted%20on%20May%2027%2C%202022.%20It%20received%20suggestions%20from%202.33%20lakh%20people%20through%2043%20public%20dialogue%20programmes%20and%20various%20mediums.%20The%20committee%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20February%202%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChairman%20of%20the%20UCC's%20rules-making%20and%20implementation%20committee%2C%20Shatrughna%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Justice%20(retd)%20Desai%20panel%2C%20said%20the%20report%20could%20not%20be%20made%20public%20earlier%20because%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20was%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20framing%20rules%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20UCC%20will%20ensure%20there%20is%20no%20breach%20of%20privacy%20of%20data%20provided%20by%20people%20at%20the%20time%20of%20registering%20their%20marriages%20and%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20he%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20a%20mandatory%20provision%20of%20informing%20the%20parents%20about%20a%20live-in%20couple%20aged%20between%2018%20and%2021%20years%20would%20not%20be%20an%20assault%20on%20their%20privacy%2C%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20formerly%20the%20chief%20secretary%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20said%20it%20was%20debatable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20of%20live-in%20couples%20above%2021%20years%20of%20age%20will%20be%20totally%20protected.%20But%2C%20for%20couples%20aged%20between%2018%20and%2021%20years%2C%20the%20committee%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20age%20(despite%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20voting%20rights)%20is%20tender%20and%20so%20the%20parents%20should%20also%20be%20kept%20in%20the%20loop%20by%20way%20of%20precaution%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20couple%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20Bill%2C%20passed%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Assembly%20on%20February%207%2C%20became%20a%20law%20with%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20giving%20her%20assent%20to%20it%20on%20March%2011.%20Uttarakhand%20is%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20after%20Independence%20to%20adopt%20such%20a%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20of%20Uttarakhand%20Act%2C%202024%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20govern%20and%20regulate%20the%20laws%20relating%20to%20marriage%20and%20divorce%2C%20succession%2C%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20inheritance%20and%20maintenance%20for%20all%20citizens%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religion%2C%20gender%2C%20caste%2C%20or%20sex.%20It%20leaves%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20out%20of%20its%20ambit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20effectively%20bans%20polygamy%20and%20%3Cem%3E'halala'%3C%2Fem%3E%20practised%20among%20a%20section%20of%20Muslims.%20Marriages%2C%20though%2C%20can%20be%20solemnised%20through%20separate%20rituals%2C%20like%20%3Cem%3Esaptapadi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Enikah%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eanand%20karaj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20followed%20by%20different%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20another%20question%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20that%20during%20the%20drafting%20committee's%20field%20visits%20to%20take%20feedback%20from%20the%20public%20on%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%2C%20about%20eight%20to%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20had%20suggested%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20population%20control%20should%20also%20be%20covered%20under%20its%20ambit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20committee%20did%20not%20include%20it%20in%20the%20report%20as%20it%20did%20not%20fall%20under%20its%20ambit.%20The%20panel%20also%20examined%20whether%20states%20had%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20bringing%20the%20UCC%20and%20found%20there%20was%20no%20Constitutional%20hurdle%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20also%20found%20that%20the%20UCC%20was%20not%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20religious%20freedom%20of%20any%20section%2C%20said%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20work%20of%20the%20rules-making%20and%20implementation%20committee%20of%20the%20UCC%20is%20in%20an%20advanced%20stage.%20%26quot%3BCoding%20of%20rules%20for%20implementation%20of%20the%20UCC%20is%20in%20progress%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20completed%20soon.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20about%20Uttarakhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami's%20recent%20comments%20that%20UCC%20will%20be%20implemented%20by%20October%20this%20year%2C%20he%20said%20the%20panel%20has%20been%20trying%20its%20best%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20law%20is%20implemented%20within%20that%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20framing%20rules%20for%20the%20UCC%2C%20which%20has%20already%20become%20an%20Act%2C%20the%20entire%20system%20of%20its%20implementation%20is%20being%20computerised%20so%20that%20people%20do%20not%20have%20any%20inconvenience%2C%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20can%20register%20marriages%20and%20live-in%20relationships%20sitting%20at%20their%20homes%20without%20going%20anywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Assembly%20passed%20the%20UCC%20Bill%2C%20the%20nine-member%20committee%20headed%20by%20Singh%20was%20formed%20to%20frame%20the%20rules%20for%20its%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20the%20makers%20of%20India's%20Constitution%20such%20as%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20and%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20Rajkumari%20Amrit%20Kaur%20and%20Minoo%20Masani%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20UCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENapoleon%20Bonaparte%20first%20introduced%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20in%20France%20in%201804%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20such%20a%20law%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Republic%20of%20T%C3%BCrkiye%20in%201926.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20being%20a%20predominantly%20Muslim%20country%2C%20it%20(T%C3%BCrkiye)%20talked%20about%20gender%20equality%20and%20banning%20polygamy%20at%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720795200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkc79p8d8_couple-generic-couple-disagreement-generic-couple-fight-istock_625x300_16_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparents-should-be-kept-informed-about-live-in-couples-aged-18-21-says-uttarakhands-ucc-panel-6091782%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20panel%20framing%20rules%20for%20Uttarakhand's%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20is%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20data%20provided%20by%20live-in%20couples%20remains%20protected%20but%20feels%20that%20information%20about%20those%20aged%2018-21%20should%20be%20given%20to%20their%20parents%2C%20the%20committee's%20chief%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparents-should-be-kept-informed-about-live-in-couples-aged-18-21-says-uttarakhands-ucc-panel-6091782%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparents-should-be-kept-informed-about-live-in-couples-aged-18-21-says-uttarakhands-ucc-panel-6091782%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparents-should-be-kept-inform