launched%20the%20first%20breast%20milk%20bank%20for%20premature%20babies%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20negotiating%20for%20it%20to%20be%20reopened%20after%20clerics%20deemed%20it%20un-Islamic%2C%20doctors%20and%20the%20national%20Islamic%20council%20said%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20milk%20bank%20in%20Karachi%20received%20religious%20approval%20in%20December%20from%20a%20provincial%20Islamic%20seminary%2C%20but%20that%20approval%20was%20withdrawn%20almost%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20facility%20opened%20in%20June%2C%20forcing%20it%20to%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBreast%20milk%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20improve%20the%20chances%20of%20the%20survival%20of%20premature%20babies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jamal%20Raza%2C%20a%20doctor%20and%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Sindh%20Institute%20of%20Child%20Health%20and%20Neonatology%20hospital%2C%20where%20the%20bank%20was%20set%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20this%20is%20about.%20Only%20premature%20babies%20were%20going%20to%20be%20given%20this%20milk%2C%26quot%3B%20Raza%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%20was%20intended%20to%20help%20premature%20babies%20survive%20in%20a%20country%20where%20the%20neonatal%20mortality%20rate%20is%2039%20deaths%20per%201%2C000%20live%20births%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20children's%20agency%20--%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20religious%20edict%2C%20or%20fatwa%2C%20approving%20the%20facility%20was%20issued%20in%20December%202023%20by%20Jamia%20Darul%20Uloom%2C%20an%20Islamic%20advisory%20body%20in%20the%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20government's%20National%20Council%20of%20Islamic%20Ideology%20later%20questioned%20whether%20it%20risked%20breaking%20Islamic%20codes%20on%20kinship%2C%20which%20dictate%20that%20husband%20and%20wife%20cannot%20be%20breastfed%20by%20the%20same%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20child's%20family%20must%20know%20who%20the%20don