0flight%20risk.%20But%20the%20government%20knows%2C%20the%20prosecutor%20knows%20that%20the%20process%20is%20the%20punishment.%20So%20they're%20delaying%20it%2C%20they%20do%20an%20insurance%20arrest.%20Now%20I%20start%20a%20ladder%20from%20the%20bottom%2C%20then%20I%20go%20to%20the%20high%20court%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20get%20relief.%20But%20you%20have%20achieved%20your%20purpose.%20You%20have%20prolonged%20(the%20stay%20in%20jail)%20by%20a%20few%20weeks...%20This%20is%20not%20the%20approach%20of%20prosecutors%2C%20it%20is%20not%20even%20the%20approach%20of%20persecutors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferencing%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20bench%20had%20also%20stated%20that%20mere%20interrogation%20cannot%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20need%20or%20necessity%26quot%3B%20for%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720792980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fud6p1t88_abhishek-manu-singhvi_625x300_12_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finsurance-arrest-abhishek-singhvi-on-cbi-action-against-arvind-kejriwal-6091943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Making%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20his%20client%2C%20senior%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20has%20said%20politics%20is%20writ%20large%20over%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20being%20arrested%20both%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finsurance-arrest-abhishek-singhvi-on-cbi-action-against-arvind-kejriwal-6091943%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finsurance-arrest-abhishek-singhvi-on-cbi-action-against-arvind-kejriwal-6091943%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finsurance-arrest-abhishek-