Schools%2C%20Muslim%20Body%20Objects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Jamiat%20Ulama-e-Hind%20has%20demanded%20withdrawal%20of%20UP%20government's%20recent%20order%20directing%20that%20all%20students%20in%20unrecognised%20madrasas%20and%20non-Muslim%20students%20studying%20in%20government-aided%20madrasas%20should%20be%20shifted%20to%20government%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20organisation%20called%20the%20order%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20secretary%2C%20Durga%20Shankar%20Mishra%2C%20in%20an%20order%20dated%20June%2026%20and%20issued%20to%20all%20the%20district%20magistrates%20of%20the%20state%2C%20cited%20a%20letter%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(NCPCR)%20dated%20June%207.%20The%20letter%20directed%20admitting%20all%20the%20non-Muslim%20students%20studying%20in%20the%20government-funded%20madrasas%20in%20the%20schools%20of%20the%20Basic%20Education%20Council%20for%20providing%20them%20formal%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%20issued%20on%20June%2026%2C%20it%20was%20also%20said%20all%20the%20children%20studying%20in%20all%20such%20madrasas%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20are%20not%20recognised%20by%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Madrasa%20Education%20Council%2C%20should%20also%20be%20given%20admission%20in%20council%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommittees%20should%20be%20formed%20at%20the%20district%20level%20by%20the%20district%20magistrates%20to%20implement%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20terming%20the%20government%20order%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20action%20violating%20the%20rights%20of%20minorities%2C%20the%20Jamiat%20Ulama-e-Hind%20has%20demanded%20its%20withdrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20on%20Thursday%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJamiat%20Ulama-e-Hind%20president%20Maulana%20Mahmood%20Asad%20Madni%20has%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Government%2C%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%2C%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%2FPrincipal%20Secretary%2C%20Minority%20Welfare%20and%20Waqf%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Director%20Minority%20Welfare%20UP%20and%20appealed%20to%20refrain%20from%20this%20unconstitutional%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20known%20that%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20correspondence%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(NCPCR)%2C%20the%20UP%20government%20has%20issued%20instructions%20on%20June%2026%2C%202024%20that%20non-Muslim%20students%20studying%20in%20aided%20and%20recognized%20madrasas%20should%20be%20separated%20and%20they%20should%20be%20admitted%20to%20government%20schools.%20Similarly%2C%20all%20the%20students%20of%20unrecognized%20madrasas%20should%20be%20forcibly%20admitted%20to%20government%20primary%20schools%20for%20modern%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20order%20will%20affect%20thousands%20of%20independent%20madrasas%20in%20the%20state%20because%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20the%20state%20where%20there%20are%20large%20independent%20madrasas%2C%20including%20Darul%20Uloom%20Deoband%20and%20Nadwatul%20Ulama%2C%20Madni%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadni%20clarified%20in%20his%20letter%20that%20NCPCR%20cannot%20give%20instructions%20to%20separate%20the%20children%20of%20aided%20madrasas%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20religion.%20This%20is%20an%20act%20of%20dividing%20the%20country%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadni%20also%20said%20the%20UP%20government%20should%20understand%20that%20madrasas%20have%20a%20separate%20legal%20identity%20and%20status%20as%20recognised%20by%20section%201(5)%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Free%20and%20Compulsory%20Education%20Act%2C%202009%20by%20exempting%20Islamic%20madrasas.%20Therefore%2C%20Jamiat%20Ulama-e-Hind%20demands%20that%20the%20government%20order%20of%20June%2026%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20has%20approximately%2025%2C000%20madrasas.%20Of%20these%2C%2016%2C000%20madrasas%20are%20government%20recognised%2C%20including%20560%20government-aided%20madrasas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20on%20April%205%20stayed%20an%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20order%2C%20which%20had%20declared%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Board%20of%20Madrasa%20Education%20Act%2C%202004%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20a%20bunch%20of%20appeals%20against%20the%20March%2022%20verdict%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%2C%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%20and%20justices%20J%20B%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20said%20the%20order%20will%20would%20impinge%20on%20the%20future%20course%20of%20education%20of%20nearly%2017%20lakh%20students%20who%20are%20pursuing%20education%20in%20these%20madrasas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Madrasa%20Education%20Council%20president%20Iftikhar%20Ahmed%20Javed%20has%20also%20reacted%20to%20the%20development%20and%20said%20no%20student%20is%20forced%20to%20study%20in%20madrasas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20non-Muslim%20students%20studying%20in%20madrasas%20are%20studying%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20their%20parents.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20forcibly%20enrolling%20them%20or%20students%20of%20unrecognised%20madrasas%20in%20council%20schools%20is%20beyond%20comprehension%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Javed%2C%20there%20are%208%2C500%20unaided%20madrasas%20in%20the%20state%20in%20which%20around%20seven%20lakh%20students%20are%20studying.%20They%20are%20proposed%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20schools%20of%20the%20Basic%20Education%20Council%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government%20order%2C%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720789920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fch2trjq_madrasa_625x300_28_July_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-to-shift-unreognised-madrasa-students-to-schools-muslim-body-objects-6091224%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Jamiat%20Ulama-e-Hind%20has%20demanded%20withdrawal%20of%20UP%20government's%20recent%20order%20directing%20that%20all%20students%20in%20unrecognised%20madrasas%20and%20non-Muslim%20students%20studying%20in%20government-aided%20madrasas%20should%20be%20shifted%20to%20government%20schools.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-to-shift-unreognised-madrasa-students-to-schools-muslim-body-objects-6091224%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-to-shift-unreognised-madrasa-students-to-schools-muslim-body-objects-6091224%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-to-shift-unreognised-madrasa-students-to-schools-muslim-body-objects-6091224%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nabard%20arm%20launches%20Rs%20750%20cr%20agri%20fund%20to%20finance%20startups%2C%20rural%20cos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720789444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2016-08%2F30%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1472559699-5975.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fnabard-arm-launches-rs-750-cr-agri-fund-to-finance-startups-rural-cos-124071200786_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20fund%20aims%20to%20promote%20investment%20in%20innovative%2C%20technology-driven%2C%20high-risk%2C%20and%20high-impact%20activities%20in%20agriculture%20and%20allied%20