lenge.%20Turning%20your%20life%20around%20and%20achieving%20something%20that%20previous%20generations%20could%20not%20is%20very%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20a%20financially%20unstable%20family%2C%20Ghosh%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20helping%20others%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20came%20to%20education.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20work%20and%20struggled%20to%20get%20an%20education.%20If%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20day%20and%20night%20to%20improve%20the%20system%20for%20the%20children%20of%20my%20village%2C%20then%20who%20will%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhosh%20has%20a%20BEd%20degree%20and%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20English%20and%20political%20science.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20working%20as%20a%20teacher%20in%201975%20and%20retired%20in%202008%20as%20an%20assistant%20teacher%20at%20Jamalpur%20High%20School%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ghosh%20was%20fresh%20out%20of%20college%2C%20ready%20to%20work%2C%20he%20had%20opened%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F125632%2Fteaching-chirag-school-rural-model%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20school%20for%20underprivileged%3C%2Fa%3E%20students%20with%20five%20of%20his%20friends.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20spirits%20were%20soon%20dulled%20by%20the%20financial%20burden%20I%20faced%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20personal%20funding.%20Working%20for%20the%20underprivileged%20meant%20lesser%20income%20for%20me.%20I%20became%20a%20family%20man%20and%20needed%20to%20support%20my%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-22-1720614800.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Basantapur%20Junior%20High%20School%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%