0CSE%20and%20IFS%20are%20different.%20While%20the%20former%20is%20on%20general%20questions%2C%20the%20latter%20stresses%20on%20technicalities%20of%20the%20forest%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20general%20answers%20might%20suffice%20in%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE)%2C%20the%20board%20for%20the%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20(IFS)%20expects%20scientific%20and%20sustainable%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harsimran%2C%20who%20secured%20210%20marks%20out%20of%20300%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347452%2Fupsc-cse-samyak-jain-visually-impaired-assistant-collector-puducherry-topper-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonality%20test%20round%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20preparing%20for%20the%20interview%2C%20I%20covered%20basic%20questions%20about%20my%20background%2C%20job%20experience%2C%20degrees%2C%20hobbies%2C%20and%20interests.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20technical%20aspects%20related%20to%20forestry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20during%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20various%20types%20of%20forest%20fires%20and%20strategies%20to%20improve%20groundwater%20quality%20affected%20by%20the%20overuse%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Harsimran%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720620910000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-1-1720617346.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D356313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20initial%20setbacks%20in%20UPSC%20CSE%20attempts%2C%20Harsimran%20Singh%20Cheema%20persisted%2C%20achieving%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2016%20in%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20UPSC%20IFS%20in%202022.%20He%20shares%20the%20difference%20in%20preparation%20strategy%20for%20IAS%20and%20IFS%2C%20sharing%20tips%20that%20worked%20for%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356313%2Fupsc-cse-ifs-officer-harsimran-singh-cheema-preparation-tips-strategy-forest-services%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Krish%20Ashok%20On%20Debunking%20Food%20Myths%20%26amp%3B%20Misinformation%20in%20His%20%E2%80%98Masala%20Lab%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20mother%20used%20to%20travel%2C%20she%20would%20jot%20down%20simple%20recipes%20like%20%3Cem%3Esambhar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20basic%20%3Cem%3Esabzis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eraitas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20curries.%20Despite%20our%20earnest%20efforts%20to%20replicate%20them%20exactly%20as%20written%2C%20my%20father%20and%20I%20could%20never%20quite%20match%20the%20taste%20of%20%3Cem%3Eamma%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20humble%20%3Cem%3Erasam%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20it%20seems%20straightforward%20but%20proves%20deceptively%20tricky%20to%20perfect.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20this%20tangy%2C%20comforting%20dish%20requires%20minimal%20ingredients%3A%20tamarind%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20crucially%2C%20the%20right%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20(which%20can%20make%20or%20break%20the%20dish!)%2C%20all%20seasoned%20with%20spices%20and%20a%20generous%20dollop%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20then%20why%20does%20my%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20never%20measure%20up%20to%20those%20made%20by%20the%20stalwarts%20of%20the%20household%3F%20Some%20might%20attribute%20it%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emaa%20ka%20pyaar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(mother%E2%80%99s%20love)%2C%20and%20while%20that%20sentiment%20holds%20true%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20scientific%20aspect%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrish%20Ashok%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20unravel%20this%20science%20and%20share%20it%20with%20the%20world.%20When%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20for%20work%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20potato%20fry%20far%20outshone%20his%20own.%20How%20does%20one%20achieve%20that%20elusive%20perfect%20crispness%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20add%20some%20spices%20after%20others%20and%20roast%20them%20for%20lesser%20times%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20because%20the%20recipe%20book%20says%20so.%20It%E2%80%99s%20due%20to%20chemical%20reactions%20that%20occur.%20The%20search%20behind%20these%20reasons%20led%20to%20Ashok%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20becoming%20a%20kitchen%20alchemist!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20780px)%20100vw%2C%20780px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashok%20with%20his%20parents%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628.jpg%20780w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-500x328.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-768x504.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-150x98.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAshok%20with%20his%20parents%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20head%20for%20AI%20Cloud%20Advisory%20and%20Consulting%20at%20TCS%20(Tata%20Consultancy%20Services)%2C%20Ashok%20applies%20his%20training%20as%20an%20engineer%20to%20decode%20the%20scien