eded%20to%20take%20your%20medicine%20dose.%20They%E2%80%99d%20organise%20your%20pills%2C%20hand%20them%20to%20you%20and%20with%20it%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20to%20make%20things%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cool%20thought%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20a%20Class%2011%20student%20at%20Navrachana%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Vadodara%20has%20innovated%3B%20albeit%20his%20creation%20is%20a%20miniaturised%2C%20robotic%20version%20of%20the%20said%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Meditel%E2%80%99%2C%20as%2015-year-old%20Nikhil%20Lemos%20has%20christened%20his%20brainchild%2C%20was%20born%20out%20of%20an%20innocent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330982%2Faditya-chaudhury-builds-neurosight-vaccivan-and-kalam-startup-to-help-student-innovators-with-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidea%20to%20help%20his%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20how%20they%20would%20sometimes%20forget%20to%20take%20their%20pills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20ideate%2C%20a%20young%20Nikhil%20put%20pen%20to%20paper%20and%20sketched%20what%20he%20assumed%20would%20be%20a%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20an%20alarm%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20was%20it%3B%20a%20doodle%20on%20the%20last%20page%20of%20a%20notebook.%20But%20a%20science%20fair%20at%20the%20end%20of%20term%20had%20him%20revisit%20this%20doodle.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20come%20up%20with%20something%20innovative%20and%20I%20thought%20of%20going%20back%20to%20this%20idea.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20Meditel%20took%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20the%20innovation%20has%20grown%20with%20Nikhil%3B%20the%20two%20have%20shared%20a%20parallel%20journey%2C%20as%20the%20idea%20transcended%20from%20being%20a%20PowerPoint%20presentation