It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20our%20sessions%20that%20he%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20make%20a%20device%20that%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312904%2Fdesigner-shreya-thakkar-innovates-wander-on-assist-smart-cane-for-the-elderly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20his%20grandfather%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20medication.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Meditel%20was%20deemed%20complete%20by%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInvention-1720583517.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356175%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeditel%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20many%20accolades%20that%20line%20Nikhil%E2%80%99s%20shelves%20%E2%80%94%20second%20runners-up%20at%20the%20Jagran%20Josh%20Education%20Awards%20in%20the%20Robotics%20Category%20(April%202024)%3B%20winner%20of%20the%20INSPIRE%20Awards%20(2023)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20national-level%20science%20fair%20organised%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%3B%20one%20of%2050%20innovators%20at%20the%20National%20Children%20Innovation%20Challenge%20in%20partnership%20with%20UNICEF%20(2023)%2C%20a%20panellist%20at%20the%20World%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Day%20Conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20(2023)%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20one%20that%20surpassed%20all%20of%20these%2C%20Nikhil%20says%2C%20was%20the%20recognition%20from%20UNICEF%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98One%20of%20the%20top%20three%20moments%20of%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn%E2%80%99t%20every%20odd%20day%20that%20you%20get%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20legend%20Beckham%20and%20relay%20your%20dreams%