eiling%2C%20but%20even%20there%2C%20men%20have%20built%20a%20glass%20ceiling%2C%20which%20she%20successfully%20broke.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20gave%20you%20the%20strength%20and%20fortitude%20to%20face%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20colleagues%20were%20nice%20to%20me%20to%20my%20face%20but%20they%20all%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20not%20capable%20just%20because%20of%20my%20gender.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20this%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fwp-admin%2Fadmin.php%3Fpage%3Dstats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproblem%20faced%20by%20women%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20land%20jobs%20too%3F%20All%20you%20can%20do%20is%20focus%20and%20work%20hard%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20keeping%20her%20chin%20up%20and%20focusing%20on%20excelling%20at%20her%20job%2C%20she%20silenced%20all%20her%20critics.%20Girls%20can%20do%20everything%2C%20she%20proved%2C%20rather%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Romeeta%20spent%20nine%20months%20on%20the%20ship%20during%20COVID-19%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-768x511.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355796%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22681%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERomeeta%20spent%20nine%20months%20on%20the%20ship%20during%20COVID-19%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20biggest%20challenge%2C%20she%20says%2C%20came%20amid%20the%20pandemic%20when%20she%20was%20stuck%20at%20sea%20for%20over%20nine%20months%20in%20China.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20she%20was%20on%20a%20cargo%20vessel%2C%20and%20with%20flights%20grounded%2C%20they%20had%20to%20stay%20on%20board%20and%20continue%20working.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20stuck%20in%20China%20and%20had%20to%20wear%20PPE%20kits%2C%20coveralls%2C%20and%20masks.%20Life%20was%20hell%20as%20we%20had%20no%20flights%20back%20home.%20It%20was%20mental%20torture%20for%20all%20of%20us%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20this%2C%20being%20on%20sea%20definitely%20comes%20with%20challenges%2C%20as%20you%20have%20to%20work%20in%20the%20engine%20room%20in%2050-55%20centigrade%20temperatures!%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20especially%20challenging%20during%20your%20%E2%80%98periods%E2%80%99.%20But%20I%20believe%20that%20you%20have%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20reach%20the%20top.%20A%20seafarer%20is%20a%20seafarer%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20gender%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20ability%20to%20rise%20above%20challenges%20led%20to%20rapid%20advancement%20in%20her%20career%2C%20as%20she%20progressed%20from%20ETO%20to%20senior%20ETO%20to%20electrical%20superintendent%20in%20just%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98At%20just%2026%2C%20I%20handled%2064%20vessels%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20first%20lady%20superintendent%20in%20Maersk%20and%20also%20the%20youngest%20one%20at%2026.%20I%20handled%2064%20vessels%20and%20provided%20electrical%20support%20and%20remote%20resolution.%20I%20was%20responsible%20for%20various%20projects%20such%20as%20LED%20lights%20in%20vessels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instg